references: In summary, the above results from Table 2, Table 3, and Figure 3 collectively confirm the effectiveness of ReCODE in enhancing the recommendation performance of different base models. We attribute this to the superiority and stability of ReCODE in modeling repeat consumption, which makes it a promising approach for improving recommender systems in real-world scenarios, particularly in cases with high repeat ratios.
